description:
Positioned within the Minnippi Quarter residential community, this beautiful residence will be a dream to come home to.

The onsite facilities included are second to none, with a 25m onsite pool, surrounded by tropical landscaping, outdoor shower and pool loungers. Nearby, you'll find the barbecue area with seating and tables. Overlooking the private section of parkland, this spot is perfect for entertaining guests. Located at the opposite end of the pool is a gym, showers and bathrooms. There is also a stunning event room which can be booked for residents' personal events. It's hard to believe you're 8 km from Brisbane CBD, when you're immersed in an environment like this. And all of this on top of extensive green spaces, bike paths and creeks of Minnippi Parklands, right on your doorstep.

Completed in 2021, 34/9 Ellen St is an architecturally designed residence. Modern and spacious, the home spans two levels of living and sleeping with just the internal garage and laundry on the lower level.

The central level is the heart of the residence, encompassing a light-filled and open plan kitchen, dining and living area. Opening out to a tropical, sun filled courtyard located directly off the living area, you'll enjoy the cross breezes drawn in from the large glass windows along the northern side of the home. High ceilings and quality finishes throughout further enhance the sense of light and space.

A modern colour palette featuring dark tones and grey tiled floors with timber accents creates a contemporary feel. The kitchen is generous in size, incorporating a 3m island bench with a waterfall edge. Quality appliances include gas cooktop with electric oven. A smoked, mirrored glass splashback adds to the urban look.

Upstairs, you'll find three generous bedrooms, all with built in robes, fans, soft light beige carpet, and quality window furnishings. The master suite has a beautiful ensuite and floor to ceiling windows. Completing this level are the family bathroom, with a deep tub.

Features at a glance –

Stunning, considered architecture
Split system air conditioning
Internal access from garage
Ample storage within garage
Low body corporate fees
On-site property manager
Extensive community amenities including pool, gym and private parkland

With such a wonderful lifestyle opportunity on offer, don't delay in viewing this luxurious home. Contact Megan today for further information.
